sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant L as Launcher<br/>(App进程)
    participant ATMS as ATMS<br/>(SystemServer)
    participant AMS as AMS<br/>(SystemServer)
    participant Z as Zygote<br/>(独立进程)
    participant App as App进程<br/>(ActivityThread)
    participant WMS as WMS<br/>(SystemServer)
    participant SF as SurfaceFlinger<br/>(Native进程)

    rect rgb(232, 245, 255)
    Note over L,ATMS: 阶段一：Launcher 发起启动请求
    L->>+ATMS: startActivity() [Binder IPC]
    Note right of ATMS: 解析Intent / 权限校验<br/>创建 ActivityRecord & TaskRecord
    ATMS-->>L: schedulePauseActivity() [Binder]
    L-->>ATMS: activityPaused() [Binder]
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
    Note over ATMS,Z: 阶段二：进程创建（Socket通信）
    ATMS->>AMS: 目标进程不存在，请求创建
    AMS->>+Z: fork请求 [Socket通信]
    Note right of Z: fork() — COW机制<br/>共享预加载的4000+类和资源
    Z->>-App: fork子进程
    Note right of App: nativeZygoteInit() → 启动Binder线程池<br/>反射调用 ActivityThread.main()
    end

    rect rgb(232, 255, 232)
    Note over App,AMS: 阶段三：App进程初始化
    Note right of App: Looper.prepareMainLooper()<br/>创建 ActivityThread 实例
    App->>+AMS: attachApplication(appThread) [Binder]
    Note right of AMS: AMS 持有 App 的 Binder 代理<br/>双向通信通道建立
    end

    rect rgb(245, 232, 255)
    Note over AMS,App: 阶段四：Application & Activity 创建
    AMS-->>App: bindApplication() [Binder回调]
    Note right of App: 创建 Instrumentation<br/>创建 Application<br/>ContentProvider.onCreate()<br/>Application.onCreate()
    AMS->>-ATMS: bindApplication完成
    ATMS-->>App: scheduleTransaction(LaunchActivityItem) [Binder]
    Note right of App: Instrumentation.newActivity() 反射创建<br/>Activity.attach() → 创建 PhoneWindow<br/>Activity.onCreate() → setContentView<br/>Activity.onStart()<br/>Activity.onResume()
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 240)
    Note over App,SF: 阶段五：首帧渲染与上屏
    App->>+WMS: WindowManager.addView(DecorView)
    Note right of App: 创建 ViewRootImpl
    WMS-->>-App: 分配 Surface
    Note right of App: 等待 Vsync 信号<br/>performTraversals()<br/>measure → layout → draw
    App->>SF: 提交 GraphicBuffer [BufferQueue]
    Note right of SF: 收集所有窗口 Layer<br/>HWC / GPU 合成
    SF->>SF: 输出到 FrameBuffer
    Note over L,SF: 首帧上屏，用户可见
    end
